snippet.title: Cilla - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cilla is a dynamic 2D side-scrolling shooter that immerses players into the complex narrative of humanity's evolution and the endless struggle for survival at any cost.

Pre-order open on Xbox and Nintendo Switch: July 24th, 2024
Release date on PlayStation, Xbox and Nintendo Switch: August 2nd, 2024
